data.description: One-Story Living!!! This  Sprawling 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath Ranch is Located on a Tree-Lined Street in the Heart of Mentor!  Newer Windows, Siding and Roof with Leaf Guards!!  Over-Sized 2.5 Car Garage with Opener!  Laundry Room & Mud Room!  Central Air!  Large Patio, Newly Paved Drive, Fully Fenced Yard with Firepit and Nice Landscaping!!  All Appliances Stay!  Great Location!!!  Original Wood-burner has been saved in garage, if needed.  Pull down steps to attic storage!  Motivated Seller!!!  Brand New Carpet and Padding throughout the entire home!
